and a future husband.

16:23.156 --> 16:25.375
You never know.

16:25.419 --> 16:27.247
Tied one on?

16:27.290 --> 16:28.988
It means she was drunk.

16:29.031 --> 16:32.339
Drunk and hopeful.
Don't you forget that.

16:32.382 --> 16:34.167
I'm learning a lot here.

16:37.474 --> 16:38.649
What the hell?

16:41.391 --> 16:43.480
Hey, pass me his beer,
would you?

16:52.228 --> 16:54.187
