17:41.060 --> 17:44.715
Wow.
That was really douchey.

17:44.759 --> 17:46.282
Sorry, I'm still in recovery.

17:46.326 --> 17:48.545
I'm gonna need you to tell me
every time I do that.

17:48.589 --> 17:52.636
